txt.en: Ost Dunhoth: Toes in the Water

The source of the poisoned waters has several places of safety. Taunt the evil there by always having each location occupied by a hero of the Free Peoples.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>This deed can only be completed on Tier 2 difficulty.</rgb>
Overcome the manifestations of poison while fully utilizing your places of safety
